snippet.title: Adrienne Janic Talks NEW Overhaulin Season 9 Premiere w/ Johnny Depp & Amber Heard
snippet.description: In the sixth #CultureCafe podcast host Will Love welcomes Adrienne Janic to the show to discuss season nine of Velocity’s “Overhaulin” premiering Wednesday November 4th 2015 at 9pm. The final season kicks off with Johnny Depp and Amber Heard. Hear all about the A-List premiere episode and new season. Adrienne also talks Velocity’s new automotive program “Competition Ready” launching in 2016 and recounts her days as a Fantana girl, television actress, supermodel and Ab Rocket extraordinaire. Plus AJ talks relationships and BFFs Brandi Glanville and Kendra Wilkinson. Find out the best luxury and economic brand vehicles and much more from this triple threat.
